Changes with tdc 1.3                                                21 Apr 2014

  * Added window title.
  * Added support for other build flags.
  * Now compiles with -Wall -Wextra -pedantic flags.
  * No more segfaults.
  * Now handles long arguments properly.
  * Current day in calendar displays correctly.
  * Makefile cleaned up.

